{"tid":1873142,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"夏天清貨？ 祖記欲賣迷失藍斯","createTime":"2020-02-10T12:56:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T11:57:01.000Z","uid":16659,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"da31fceeffccd2c0c83eb6745b7181bd92397da9","tid":1873142,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T12:56:52.000Z","msg":"根據英國《每日郵報》報道，意甲班霸祖雲達斯有意在今夏清洗陣中瘀血，去夏以自由身來投的威爾斯國腳中場艾朗藍斯就是球隊的清洗對象之一。<br />\n<br />\n現年29歲的藍斯在去夏以自由身由效力11個球季的阿仙奴加盟祖雲達斯，周薪高達40萬鎊。但因為傷患和戰術問題，他只在意甲上陣12場(共569分鐘)，攻入一球，但當中不少是後備上陣。沙利在中場的位置上更屬意起用賓坦古亞、拉比奧特、比真歷和基迪拉，技術功底略遜的藍斯明顯不是沙利那杯茶。<br />\n<br />\n藍斯在意甲只上陣569分鐘下，已花費了祖雲達斯320萬鎊的薪金開支。在球隊陣容過於龐大下，祖雲達斯打算讓這名威爾斯「二當家」離隊，以開源節流減省支出，此子的估價亦達到4000萬歐元。除了藍斯外，另一名由英超以自由身來投的中場安尼簡已在冬窗離開球隊，以外借的形式加盟多蒙特，此子亦在處子戰中建功轟入一記絕妙的世界波。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：<a href=\"https://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-7983817/Juventus-planning-sell-Aaron-Ramsey-year-signing-midfielder-Arsenal.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2Farticle-7983817%2FJuventus-planning-sell-Aaron-Ramsey-year-signing-midfielder-Arsenal.html&d=u5wkwi0qRaq%2FdbVqa5yG4aVJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=aa356779\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-7983817/Juventus-planning-sell-Aaron-Ramsey-year-signing-midfielder-Arsenal.html</a>"},{"pid":"2e63dd9e981732886cf6ae3367ca2ea9fe2eb884","tid":1873142,"uid":283207,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T12:57:42.000Z","msg":"回家吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83d076b6fb26f46e1987df1e35265d69c0274aae","tid":1873142,"uid":20611,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"2e63dd9e981732886cf6ae3367ca2ea9fe2eb884","tid":1873142,"uid":283207,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T12:57:42.000Z","msg":"回家吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T12:58:38.000Z","msg":"返卡迪夫吧<i